114.8]}, {"text": "198", "bbox": [969.1, 1092.6, 995.6, 1114.8]}, {"text": "831", "bbox": [1118.1, 1092.6, 1144.7, 1114.8]}, {"text": "December 31, 2015  (e)", "bbox": [116.5, 1121.2, 278.2, 1143.4]}, {"text": "321", "bbox": [668.8, 1121.2, 695.4, 1143.4]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [828.6, 1121.2, 844.5, 1143.4]}, {"text": "147", "bbox": [969.1, 1121.2, 1011.5, 1143.4]}, {"text": "468", "bbox": [1118.2, 1121.2, 1144.7, 1143.4]}, {"text": "(a)", "bbox": [85.9, 1152.2, 107.3, 1172.1]}, {"text": "Natural gas volumes have been converted to barrels of oil equivalent (BOE) based on energy content of six thousand cubic feet (Mcf) of gas to one barrel of oil.", "bbox": [122.7, 1152.2, 1149.7, 1172.1]}, {"text": "Barrels of oil equivalence does not necessarily result in price equivalence.  The price of natural gas on a barrel of oil equivalent basis is currently substantially lower", "bbox": [122.7, 1173.0, 1145.7, 1192.9]}, {"text": "than the corresponding price for oil and has been similarly lower for a number of years.  For example, in 2015, the average prices of West Texas Intermediate (WTI)", "bbox": [122.7, 1193.8, 1145.8, 1213.7]}, {"text": "oil and New York Mercantile Exchange (NYMEX) natural gas were $48.80 per barrel and $2.75 per Mcf, respectively, resulting in an oil to gas ratio of 18 to 1.", "bbox": [122.7, 1214.7, 1108.6, 1234.6]}, {"text": "(b)", "bbox": [85.9, 1235.5, 107.3, 1255.4]}, {"text": "Includes proved reserves related to PSCs and other similar economic arrangements of 0.5 billion BOE, 0.7 billion BOE, 0.8 billion BOE and 0.8 billion BOE, at", "bbox": [122.7, 1235.5, 1145.8, 1255.4]}, {"text": "December 31, 2015, 2014, 2013,  and 2012, respectively.", "bbox": [122.7, 1256.3, 484.1, 1276.2]}, {"text": "(c)", "bbox": [85.9, 1277.2, 106.5, 1297.0]}, {"text": "Revisions of previous estimates were primarily price and price-related.", "bbox": [122.7, 1277.2, 565.0, 1297.0]}, {"text": "(d)", "bbox": [85.9, 1298.0, 107.3, 1317.9]}, {"text": "Approximately 11 percent of the proved developed reserves at December 31, 2015 are nonproducing, primarily associated with Permian EOR.", "bbox": [122.7, 1298.0, 1016.7, 1317.9]}, {"text": "(e)", "bbox": [85.9, 1318.8, 107.3, 1338.7]}, {"text": "A portion of the proved undeveloped reserves associated with the Al Hosn gas project is expected to be developed beyond five years and is tied to an approved long", "bbox": [122.7, 1318.8, 1145.8, 1338.7]}, {"text": "term development project.", "bbox": [122.7, 1339.6, 291.2, 1359.5]}, {"text": ",", "bbox": [85.9, 1402.1, 89.9, 1422.0]}]}